Package: MatchOmics
Type: Package
Title: Propensity Score Matching Framework for Heterogeneity-Aware Omics Association Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Nam-Eun",
           family = "Kim",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "garameunn@gmail.com")
Description: Provides propensity score matching and weighted GEE-based association testing
    for heterogeneity-aware omics analysis. The package supports microbiome, proteome,
    metabolome, transcriptome, and other omics data by allowing omics-specific
    heterogeneity indices for propensity score estimation.
